						               													<description>Perjuangan Jomblo (&amp;quot;Singles Struggles&amp;quot;) is an Indonesian-designed board game, portraying the struggles of men and women in Indonesia finding the love of their life.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Perjuangan Jomblo finished on the third place of Kompas Board Game Challange 2015, behind Waroong Wars and Pagelarang Yogyakarta as first and second place respectively.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The goal of the game is to achieve a set number of victory points by making a move to a set of men/women with different needs. Each round, players are taking turn in selecting a man or woman to make a move to. They fulfill the needs of their target by playing cards from their hands. Afterwards, there is an added push your luck element by guessing the required &amp;quot;cool&amp;quot; or &amp;quot;handsome&amp;quot; factor from the randomizer deck. IF they are successful, some VP is awarded, and the target goes up to the next level (more needy), making them harder to be approached next time. The empty slot below him/her is then filled with a new one at the end of the round.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The game also features a little bit of take-that mechanism to ruin other player's relationship.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;user summary&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Wahai Pejuang Cinta !!!&amp;#10;Kini tiba saatnya untukmu maju bertempur di medan cinta. Berjuanglah untuk mengejar pujaan hatimu demi mendapatkan cinta mereka. Ini bukanlah pertarungan yang sepele, ini akan keras! Penuh intrik dan perjuangan.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Mampukah kamu lulus dari gelar Jomblo ? Tunjukan perjuangan cintamu dalam board game Perjuangan Jomblo.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from publisher&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
